00:36:52,560 --> 00:36:55,680
Mga puwersa ng kasamaan, mabuklod kayo sa tronong ito

478
00:36:56,120 --> 00:37:00,080
na parang itinakda ng langit!

479
00:37:24,680 --> 00:37:25,760
Nakulong ang enerhiya niya!

480
00:37:26,160 --> 00:37:27,360
Nagsimula na ang pagbubuklod.

481
00:37:33,520 --> 00:37:34,720
Tuloy lang!

482
00:37:34,760 --> 00:37:35,600
Kaya ko ito!

483
00:38:21,320 --> 00:38:21,720
Matatalo?

484
00:38:21,960 --> 00:38:22,280
Tao?

485
00:38:24,920 --> 00:38:25,640
Niran?

486
00:38:42,800 --> 00:38:44,120
Nakuha tayo nito, 'di ba?

487
00:38:45,440 --> 00:38:46,200
Ulap?

488
00:38:47,160 --> 00:38:48,720
Mula sa lahat ng mga alamat
na aming sinaliksik,

489
00:38:49,680 --> 00:38:53,200
Ang pinakamalakas na kapangyarihan ni Qi Rong ay
ang kanyang manipulasyon ng hamog.

490
00:38:53,680 --> 00:38:56,200
Kung gayon, paano natin ito lalabanan?

491
00:38:58,480 --> 00:38:59,760
Anuman ang mangyari,

492
00:39:00,880 --> 00:39:03,120
kailangan nating ituloy ang ritwal.

493
00:39:49,600 --> 00:39:50,640
Pete!

494
00:39:51,360 --> 00:39:52,480
Niran!

495
00:40:27,240 --> 00:40:27,760
Kalokohan!

496
00:40:28,480 --> 00:40:29,200
Tao?

497
00:40:29,520 --> 00:40:30,520
Oo, ako 'to.

498
00:40:30,840 --> 00:40:31,920
Ikaw ang unang taong natagpuan ko!

499
00:40:33,160 --> 00:40:33,800
Tao!

500
00:40:35,720 --> 00:40:36,520
Matatalo?

501
00:40:37,640 --> 00:40:38,840
Kayo ang unang nakasalubong ko.

502
00:40:39,400 --> 00:40:41,120
Kung susundin natin ang tunog ng tambol,

503
00:40:43,080 --> 00:40:44,560
baka sakaling mahanap natin
ang daan pabalik sa lahat.

504
00:40:45,000 --> 00:40:45,480
Taya ko!

505
00:40:46,240 --> 00:40:47,720
Natatandaan mo ba ang sinabi nila?

506
00:40:48,040 --> 00:40:51,760
Kung magtutulungan tayong lahat at tatapusin
ang ritwal, makakamit natin ito.

507
00:40:52,120 --> 00:40:52,880
Hindi lang iyon.

508
00:40:54,480 --> 00:40:55,040
- Pete.
- Pete.

509
00:40:59,560 --> 00:41:01,160
Kinulong tayo ng demonyo dito.

510
00:41:02,640 --> 00:41:04,480
Ang tanging paraan para maalis ang hamog na ito

511
00:41:05,040 --> 00:41:06,520
ay ang pagbibigay ng sakripisyo sa demonyo.

512
00:41:12,760 --> 00:41:14,520
Trabaho mo iyan.

513
00:41:23,400 --> 00:41:24,160
Hoy!

514
00:41:25,040 --> 00:41:26,400
May tao ba roon?

515
00:41:52,280 --> 00:41:54,880
Asong-labada!

516
00:41:55,320 --> 00:41:57,000
- Asong kuting!
- Asong kuting!

517
00:41:57,320 --> 00:41:59,000
- Asong kuting!
- Asong kuting!

518
00:41:59,800 --> 00:42:01,480
- Asong kuting!
- Asong kuting!

519
00:42:02,040 --> 00:42:03,720
- Asong kuting!
- Asong kuting!

520
00:42:03,920 --> 00:42:04,960
LAPDOG!
KUNG WALA ANG MGA STRING,
ISANG WALANG KULUNGANG PUPPET KA LANG.

521
00:42:04,960 --> 00:42:06,080
MGA GAWAD PARA SA PINAKAMAHUSAY NA LAPDOG NG SCUMBAG

522
00:42:06,520 --> 00:42:08,200
- Asong kuting!
- Asong kuting!

523
00:42:08,560 --> 00:42:10,080
LAPDOG NG PAMAHALAAN
LAPDOG!

524
00:42:10,160 --> 00:42:11,280
- Asong kuting!
- Asong kuting!

525
00:42:11,680 --> 00:42:12,800
- Asong kuting!
- Asong kuting!

526
00:42:12,800 --> 00:42:13,760
- Asong-alaga!

527
00:43:26,040 --> 00:43:27,120
Wu Yong Le!

528
00:44:03,200 --> 00:44:03,720
WHO?

529
00:44:04,160 --> 00:44:04,840
Ang Wu.

530
00:44:21,880 --> 00:44:22,640
Niran.

531
00:44:23,240 --> 00:44:24,360
Bakit hindi mo ito suot?

532
00:44:25,520 --> 00:44:26,360
Ako ang nagdisenyo nito.

533
00:44:26,520 --> 00:44:27,280
Lahat ay nakasuot nito.

534
00:44:29,880 --> 00:44:30,960
Aba, tingnan mo.

535
00:44:31,480 --> 00:44:32,400
Nakakainis talaga.

536
00:44:32,480 --> 00:44:33,000
Sino ba naman ang gugustuhing magsuot niyan?

537
00:44:33,040 --> 00:44:33,440
Hoy.

538
00:44:34,320 --> 00:44:35,600
Bawiin mo.

539
00:44:36,760 --> 00:44:38,040
Ang astig talaga.

540
00:44:38,240 --> 00:44:40,600
Kung sa tingin mo ay astig,
mas nakakahiya pa.

541
00:44:40,960 --> 00:44:41,400
Ano ba 'yan? / Ano ba 'yan?

542
00:44:42,040 --> 00:44:43,320
Bakit mo nilalagay ang 'the' sa unahan ng 'Wu'?

543
00:44:46,160 --> 00:44:46,480
Tingnan mo.

544
00:44:49,520 --> 00:44:49,920
Ano?

545
00:44:50,760 --> 00:44:52,360
Mula sa likuran, nagtatanong ito, "Sino?"

546
00:44:52,960 --> 00:44:53,880
Gaya ng, "Sino ako?"

547
00:44:54,520 --> 00:44:55,360
Tapos lumingon ka…

548
00:44:58,360 --> 00:44:59,320
"Ako si Wu!"

549
00:45:01,240 --> 00:45:02,520
Ngayon gusto mo isuot 'yan, 'di ba?

550
00:45:02,880 --> 00:45:04,960
Pinag-isipan ko nang mabuti ang lahat, pare.

551
00:45:05,000 --> 00:45:06,160
Nagdududa ako. Sigurado akong naisip mo lang 'yan.

552
00:45:06,160 --> 00:45:07,400
Sinasadya 'yon, tanga.

553
00:45:07,600 --> 00:45:08,080
Tingnan mo.

554
00:45:08,560 --> 00:45:10,560
Magmumukha ba itong ganito ka-cool kung hindi?

555
00:45:10,720 --> 00:45:11,400
Kalokohan ito.

556
00:45:11,440 --> 00:45:12,040
Isuot mo.

557
00:45:12,280 --> 00:45:13,040
Ang hirap sana kung ganun.

558
00:45:13,080 --> 00:45:15,280
- Isuot mo!
- Naku, pare? Hindi pwede!

559
00:45:15,680 --> 00:45:16,040
Isuot mo na!

560
00:45:16,040 --> 00:45:16,400
Pete!

561
00:45:16,720 --> 00:45:18,880
- Pagtutulungan 'yan, pare!
- Huwag mo akong bigyan ng tropeo!

562
00:45:19,080 --> 00:45:20,320
Mag-ingat ka diyan! Akin 'yan!

563
00:45:20,480 --> 00:45:21,480
- Isuot mo na ngayon din.
- Hindi maganda!

564
00:45:22,080 --> 00:45:22,720
Ang astig!

565
00:45:22,960 --> 00:45:23,800
Isuot mo na, tanga!

566
00:45:24,120 --> 00:45:24,600
Hubarin mo ang damit mo!

567
00:45:29,840 --> 00:45:30,640
Gwapo talaga.

568
00:45:31,440 --> 00:45:32,200
Ang Wu.

569
00:45:32,720 --> 00:45:33,840
Kami ang Wu!

570
00:45:34,840 --> 00:45:36,200
Naku, baka masyadong magulo ito.

571
00:45:36,800 --> 00:45:37,600
Ang astig talaga.

572
00:45:38,280 --> 00:45:38,600
Aba?

573
00:45:39,400 --> 00:45:40,720
Masaya ka na ngayon?

574
00:45:41,120 --> 00:45:41,680
Kapit lang.

575
00:45:43,280 --> 00:45:43,960
Magpakuha tayo ng litrato.

576
00:45:45,120 --> 00:45:45,760
Ang astig lang talaga namin.

577
00:45:47,000 --> 00:45:47,520
Halika rito.

578
00:45:49,080 --> 00:45:50,800
Heto. Mas maganda ang anggulong ito.

579
00:45:51,760 --> 00:45:54,040
Isa, dalawa, tatlo.

580
00:45:54,920 --> 00:45:57,640
Hoy, huwag mong takpan ang logo!

581
00:45:57,880 --> 00:45:58,840
Ang Wu! Pagtutulungan!

582
00:45:59,040 --> 00:45:59,880
Bakit hindi ka nakikipagtulungan
sa team, pare?

583
00:45:59,920 --> 00:46:01,440
Maging masaya ka na lang na isinuot ko pa.

584
00:46:01,600 --> 00:46:02,640
Bakit pa tayo kumukuha ng mga litrato?

585
00:46:02,840 --> 00:46:04,480
Huwag mong guluhin.

586
00:46:04,640 --> 00:46:05,040
Tara na.

587
00:46:05,240 --> 00:46:06,280
Isa, dalawa, tatlo.

588
00:46:16,720 --> 00:46:19,360
Kung aatras tayo ngayon, ibig sabihin...

589
00:46:20,000 --> 00:46:21,600
Panalo ang demonyo, 'di ba?

590
00:46:27,840 --> 00:46:29,600
Sa puntong ito, hindi maikakaila na

591
00:46:31,640 --> 00:46:32,920
ano ang gagawin natin

592
00:46:34,520 --> 00:46:35,600
ay lubos na nagbabanta sa buhay.
